OL,6,FThey ordered #99.40 of food and drink
OL,7,Ffrom the Golden Fortune takeaway in
OL,8,FPort Talbot without paying on January
OL,9,F31, doing the same with #276.60 worth
OL,10,Fof meals from La Casona restaurant in
OL,11,FSkewen on February 23.
OL,13,FOn March 27, the couple dishonestly
OL,14,Fobtained #196 of food and drink from
OL,15,FIsabella's in Porthcawl. They
OL,16,Fcommitted the same offence again on
OL,17,FApril 19, taking #329.10 of food and
OL,18,Fdrink from Bella Ciao in Swansea.
