OL,6,FThe case emerged after newly-opened
OL,7,FBella Ciao in Swansea reported that a
OL,8,Ffamily had left without paying a bill
OL,9,Fworth #329.
OL,11,FWriting on Facebook, the restaurant
OL,12,Fdescribed how a woman tried to pay
OL,13,Fwith a savings account card which was
OL,14,Fdeclined twice.
OL,16,FShe then told staff her son would wait
OL,17,Finside while she went to fetch a
OL,18,Fdifferent card.
