OL,6,FThe River House also posted on
OL,7,FFacebook about the couple, stating
OL,8,Fthat they had racked up a #270 bill
OL,9,Fbefore leaving without paying.
OL,11,FWriting last August, the restaurant
OL,12,Fsaid: "They run up a very hefty bill
OL,13,F(for 5) and 'promised' to get cash
OL,14,Ffrom the local cash point after their
OL,15,Fcard got declined.
OL,17,F"We like to put trust in some people,
OL,18,Fbut this was obviously carefully
OL,19,Fplanned as they all just disappeared."
