OL,6,FDavid Chapman, executive director for
OL,7,FUK Hospitality in Wales, said so-
OL,8,Fcalled "dining and dashing" is a
OL,9,F"constant problem" the hospitality
OL,10,Fsector faces.
OL,12,FHe said: "There are an awful lot of
OL,13,Fhonest people out there that enjoy
OL,14,Fusing our hospitality premises, but it
OL,15,Fdoes happen. UK Hospitality estimates
OL,16,Fthat every year this type of behaviour
OL,17,Fcosts businesses as much as #10million
OL,18,Fin Wales.
