OL,3,CCouple jailed after racking up large
OL,4,Cbills at restaurants without paying
OL,6,F"It's heartbreaking when people put so
OL,7,Fmuch effort and so much of their life
OL,8,Finto creating the dishes people enjoy.
OL,10,F"It's not just stealing food, it's
OL,11,Fstealing business sustainability. It's
OL,12,Fstealing staff benefits. It's stealing
OL,13,Fthe enjoyment of others.
OL,15,F"Because these businesses have to
OL,16,Fsurvive, have to grow, have to invest.
OL,17,FYou may think it's a small amount of
OL,18,Fmoney but even with one dine and dash
OL,19,Fit can impact on profit margins for a
OL,20,Fbusiness and cause problems that will
OL,21,Fimpact on other parts of the business."
